data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This exquisite two-story residence offers a perfect blend of contemporary style and functionality, with 4 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms to accommodate the needs of a growing family or those who love to entertain. Upon entering, you'll be captivated by the spacious and inviting living room featuring tall ceilings that create an airy atmosphere. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living room to a chef's delight kitchen, complete with a large island, perfect for casual dining or hosting friends and family. The first floor also boasts a conveniently located bedroom, ideal for guests or as a versatile space for a home gym or playroom. Discover the convenience of a well-appointed laundry room on the first floor, making daily chores a breeze. The adjacent dining room and dedicated office space provide flexibility for various lifestyle needs, whether you work from home or enjoy hosting formal dinners. As you ascend the staircase, you'll find three additional bedrooms on the second floor. The primary bedroom is a true retreat, offering ample space, a luxurious bathroom, and a sitting area that has been converted into extra closet space! Entertainment possibilities abound with a large loft space on the second floor, perfect for a game room, home theater, or a quiet reading nook. The two-car garage is not only convenient but also future-ready, as it comes wired for an electric vehicle charger. Located in a desirable neighborhood, this home provides both comfort and style, making it an exceptional opportunity for those seeking the perfect blend of modern living and thoughtful design. Don't miss the chance to make this stunning property your new home! Schedule a tour today to experience the beauty and functionality this residence has to offer.
